content:
The Central Bank of Russia is working on integrating crypto assets into the local financial system.<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
The CBR released a <a href="https://www.cbr.ru/Content/Document/File/141991/Consultation_Paper_07112022.pdf" data-v-f87c67ca="">report</a> on digital assets, focusing on integrating them into financial systems. Main areas of concern included proper taxation and regulation of digital asset issuance — familiar themes in crypto regulatory discussions worldwide.&nbsp;
